entries.complete: pcontrast1 Storm Squadron Command:pcontrast3 <The Rebels managed to recover the false information while you were fighting the A-wings. Scan indicate increased activity around the ambush point.>
entries.split_quest_alert: The Rebels have captured the decoy shuttle! The false information on it should lead them right into our ambush. Travel to the ambush point and wait for the Rebels to arrive. Maintain control of that position until we can get a full sensor scan of the surrounding area.
entries.title: Endor System: Destroy the Rebel Strikeforce
entries.title_d: Destroy the Rebel A-wings that have been sent to eliminate you. Making sure that they are all eliminated will help in selling the deception.
